# Journey-phase operating protocol

**SSOT:** [docs/architecture/admincn-frontend-preflight.md](docs/architecture/admincn-frontend-preflight.md) for AdminCN-hosted phases; Feed Farm Trade ops: [docs/fft/RUNTIME.md](docs/fft/RUNTIME.md). Route map: [doc/frontend/03-routes.md](doc/frontend/03-routes.md).

Before writing any product code, run this seven-step gate:

---

## Step 1 â€” Name the phase

Pick exactly one:

| Phase ID              | Canonical routes                                                                           |
| --------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| `pre-login`           | `/` `/auth/*` `/org/login` `/client/login` `/invite/[token]` `/f/[token]` `/survey/[slug]` |
| `join`                | `/join?invitationId=`                                                                      |
